      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"RazorBackShadingPt.1-Shading\">Shading</h3><p>For the Lookdev scene, prioritize using neutral lighting, adhering to classic Lookdev principles, utilizing chrome balls/grey balls, and using a Macbeth chart. </p><p>Implement a key light, a backlight, and an HDRI from <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://polyhaven.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Polyhaven</a> to serve as a fill light and establish the boundaries of a studio environment. </p><p>While maintaining neutrality, feel free to infuse a personal touch into your Lookdev scene. This not only sets the stage for shading your assets but also enhances the presentation, making it more compelling for potential professional studios or clients.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"renderman_lookdevscene.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/renderman_lookdevscene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596988967&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=308\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657228220/renderman_lookdevscene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596988967&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"377\" data-width=\"928\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657424680\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"renderman_lookdevscene.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657228220\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"8599ab5b-397b-41b2-8e6d-0bdc7a384f59\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/renderman_lookdevscene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596988967&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1237&amp;height=502 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/renderman_lookdevscene.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762596988967&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=308 1x\"></span><p>Regularly switch light rigs during the shading process to ensure the asset remains as neutral as possible, adaptable to various environments and lighting conditions. </p><p>This approach minimizes the need for extensive shader adjustments for each shot. </p><p>Use HDRI environments, such as full-sun and diffuse-gray-sky, to fine-tune your shaders effectively.</p><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>TIP: Make several tabs in which you can store all your shaders and move around your hypershade more quickly.</p>\n</div></div><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shading_organisation.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/shading_organisation.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762597063941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=299\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657228220/shading_organisation.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762597063941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"379\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"656998890\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shading_organisation.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657228220\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"d8ff7f96-be42-4fc1-858e-2e96af4cd1e4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/shading_organisation.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762597063941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=505 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657228220/shading_organisation.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762597063941&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=299 1x\"></span><p />"
